{"type":"message","id":"cefa6059","parentId":"7b5af669","timestamp":"2026-04-27T18:04:53.538Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uf5rqo18izh9_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2m2026-04-27T18:04:53.173371Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T18:04:53.181126Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T18:04:53.181154Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T18:04:53.181179Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1002,"aggregated":"[2m2026-04-27T18:04:53.173371Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T18:04:53.181126Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...